552, 2.1538, 2.153, 2.1533, 2.1538, 2.1532, 2.1552, 2.1405, 2.1293, 2.1307, 2.119, 2.1104, 2.1281, 2.1312, 2.13, 2.1391, 2.1389, 2.1429, 2.1432, 2.139, 2.1392, 2.1397, 2.1405, 2.1387, 2.1427, 2.1413, 2.1445, 2.1497, 2.1528, 2.1544, 2.1586, 2.1589, 2.1556, 2.1563, 2.1574, 2.1552, 2.1541, 2.1604, 2.1583, 2.1572, 2.1572, 2.1519, 2.1552, 2.1569, 2.1554, 2.1512, 2.1498, 2.148, 2.1516, 2.1524, 2.155, 2.1471, 2.148, 2.154, 2.1542, 2.1524, 2.1591, 2.1632, 2.1647, 2.1642, 2.1661, 2.1653, 2.1625, 2.1634, 2.1629, 2.1654, 2.1602, 2.169, 2.1695, 2.1685, 2.1705, 2.1708, 2.1715, 2.1684, 2.1661, 2.1707, 2.1657, 2.1657, 2.1628, 2.165, 2.1642, 2.1676, 2.1768, 2.1788, 2.1801, 2.183, 2.1871, 2.1921, 2.1939, 2.1967, 2.199, 2.1924, 2.1907, 2.1933, 2.1915, 2.1913, 2.1921, 2.1896, 2.1903, 2.1896, 2.1942, 2.1957, 2.2003, 2.1997, 2.1985, 2.2029, 2.1945, 2.1915, 2.1922, 2.1869, 2.1947, 2.1952, 2.1943, 2.1908, 2.1934, 2.1939, 2.1971, 2.1885, 2.1861, 2.1933, 2.1885, 2.1779, 2.1785, 2.1759, 2.1717, 2.1794, 2.1782, 2.1738, 2.1784, 2.1792, 2.1822, 2.1812, 2.1792, 2.1754, 2.1771, 2.1829, 2.1805, 2.1805, 2.1878, 2.1935, 2.1907, 2.1841, 2.1993, 2.2036, 2.1991, 2.2019, 2.2008, 2.2061, 2.2041, 2.2003, 2.2009, 2.2106, 2.2096, 2.204, 2.2004, 2.2039, 2.2008, 2.1887, 2.1873, 2.201, 2.1915, 2.1926, 2.1919, 2.1979, 2.204, 2.2027, 2.2086, 2.2027, 2.1935, 2.1886], "summary_html": "<h1>商品期货展期收益策略初探</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>该策略利用商品期货的展期收益率（roll yield）进行截面多空交易。核心逻辑是：处于现货升水（backwardation）状态的品种具有正的展期收益，趋势延续概率更高，应做多；处于现货贴水（contango）状态的品种则做空。通过对所有品种的展期收益率进行截面排名，做多排名靠前的品种、做空排名靠后的品种，捕获 carry 溢价。该策略与传统趋势策略相关性低（高胜率低盈亏比 vs 低胜率高盈亏比），具有良好的互补性。</p>\n<p>复现中采用双信号组合（ry 滚动均值 + ryminusema252）替代单一信号，显著提升了稳定性。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.19</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>8.9%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>7.4%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-16.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3391</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.39</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.52</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.58 / 1.32</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.29</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.18</span></td><td>1.66</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.76</span></td><td>0.27</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.44</span></td><td>1.31</td><td>1.25</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.27</span></td><td>0.81</td><td>1.69</td><td>1.21</td><td>0.77</td><td>1.41</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.26</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ryminusema252</code></td><td>展期收益EMA</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ifjy</code></td><td>是否交易</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 15 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 15 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>56</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3393</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>100.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>38.8</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>展期收益率定义：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">R_t = \\frac{\\ln(P_{t,n}) - \\ln(P_{t,d})}{N_{t,d} - N_{t,n}} \\times 365</div>\n<p>其中：</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">P_{t,n}</span>: 近月合约价格（主力合约）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">P_{t,d}</span>: 远月合约价格（次主力合约）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">N_{t,n}, N_{t,d}</span>: 近月/远月距交割日天数</li>\n</ul>\n<p>信号平滑与组合：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\bar{R}_t^{(i)} = \\frac{1}{\\text{CprLen}} \\sum_{k=0}^{\\text{CprLen}-1} R_{t-k}^{(i)}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo}_t^{(i)} = \\frac{1}{2}\\left[\\text{rank}_{\\text{cs}}(\\bar{R}_t^{(i)}) + \\text{rank}_{\\text{cs}}(\\text{ryema252}_t^{(i)})\\right]</div>\n<p>仓位信号：做多 combo rank &gt; (1 - TopRate) 的品种，做空 combo rank &lt;= TopRate 的品种。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>单信号 R180/H10/IC gate，Sharpe 1.14；evidence gate 失败</td><td>基线建立：使用真实 ry 数据 + IC gate 过滤弱品种</td><td>Sharpe 1.14，远超研报原文 0.55</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>CS IC=0.020，TS IC~0；turnover 5.7% 合理</td><td>新增 combo 变体（ry 滚动均值 + ryminusema252 双排名组合）+ 连续仓位变体 + 填充 evidence_pack</td><td>combo 提升至 Sharpe 1.20，连续仓位 1.05</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>combo 已是最优信号类型，探索参数空间</td><td>combo 参数网格：CprLen {150,180}, HoldLen {10,15}, TopRate {0.15,0.2}</td><td><strong>combo_R180_H15_ic_cs = 1.31</strong>，combo_R150_H10_ic_raw = 1.30</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R2 引入双信号组合（ry_rm + ryminusema252）是提升 Sharpe 的关键。两个信号捕获 carry 的不同维度 -- ry 滚动均值反映绝对水平，ryminusema252 反映相对于长期趋势的偏离。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货（约 56 个活跃品种，ry 非空约 40 个/日）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 15 个交易日换仓</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 展期收益率（ry）非空率约 37%，仅部分品种/日期有数据\n<p>- 与因子库中 dongzhen carry 因子相关系数 0.63，属于 carry 类因子族 - 时序 IC 接近零，策略依赖截面排名差异而非品种内趋势 - 2016、2019、2024 年 Sharpe 接近零，策略在 carry 溢价收敛期表现较弱</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>CPR_LEN</code></td><td><code>180</code></td><td>rolling mean window for ry</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_LEN</code></td><td><code>15</code></td><td>rebalance interval (days)</td></tr><tr><td><code>TOP_RATE</code></td><td><code>0.2</code></td><td>long/short threshold (top/bottom 20%)</td></tr><tr><td><code>VOL_TGT</code></td><td><code>0.20</code></td><td>volatility target</td></tr><tr><td><code>MAX_LEV</code></td><td><code>2.0</code></td><td>max leverage per symbol</td></tr><tr><td><code>VOL_WIN</code></td><td><code>40</code></td><td>vol estimation window</td></tr><tr><td><code>MIN_SYMS</code></td><td><code>5</code></td><td>min symbols per cross-section</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.23s</li>\n</ul>"}